This directory contains a test converter which is capable of generating
binary test input for the benchmark program

* Note * For Risk Management, the ascii input is in the csv files. Because
this is historical data we do not randomly generate it.

To run this test generator, 
First, 

cd ..
source link.sh
cd testGen
make clean; make DEC_DATATYPE=$DEC_DATATYPE WIDTH=$BITWIDTH

Then followed by

 ** Edit inputs.txt with $PREFIX.txt **
./CONVERTER.$DEC_DATATYPE 

When you run this program, it will read all the files in the ascii directory
and convert them to corresponding binary files in the bin/ directory.
Use the binary file for the benchmark simulation and ascii output file
for your reference.
